    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ Lord, though Thou didst stand be-fore__ the tri-bu---nal, en-dur-ing judg---ment at Pi-late’s hands,__ Thou didst__ not de-part from Thy___ Fa---ther, seat-ed with__ Him__ on Thy throne a-bove.__ And Thou didst rise____ from the__ dead, O Friend__ of__ man most__ mer-ci-ful,__ free-ing the world from the bit--ter__ bond---age__ of the al--i-en and en----e----my."
